📌 How to Use
Clone or download this repository.

Open index.html in any modern web browser.

Explore how semantic tags and accessibility practices are used.

💡 Learning Outcomes
Learn how to structure an HTML document semantically.

Understand the importance of accessibility in web development.

Apply basic SEO principles for better search engine visibility.
